        comparaisonTransport: "The TGV Lyon Part-Dieu — Montélimar takes about 1h10 for a ticket of €20 to €45 depending on the period. The TER is less frequent and takes about 1h45 for around €25. BlaBlaCar offers rides between €12 and €18 per passenger. By personal car, budget €18 for fuel and €16.80 for tolls, about €35 excluding parking. The TaxiNeo taxi at €210 — €260 for 1 to 4 passengers offers door-to-door comfort and avoids the stress of driving on the A7, especially in summer. For a family of 4 travelling with luggage, the cost per person (€52 to €65) is competitive against the TGV, especially when adding the journey from station to final destination.",
